Package com.intellij.structuralsearch.plugin.ui

Class StructuralSearchDialog

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.openapi.ui.DialogWrapper
      • com.intellij.structuralsearch.plugin.ui.StructuralSearchDialog
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DocumentListener, ProjectManagerListener, java.util.EventListener

    public class StructuralSearchDialog
extends DialogWrapper
implements ProjectManagerListener, DocumentListener
    This dialog is used in two ways: 1. a non-modal search dialog, showing a scope panel 2. a modal edit dialog for Structural Search inspection patterns
